Team of Investors | Pamlico Capital
































Our Team
A seasoned team of professionals with a focus on prudent investing and maintaining the highest ethical standards





Investing for the Long Term
For more than 25 years, the Pamlico Capital team has generated consistently high returns for our investors by partnering with outstanding lower middle market businesses. Our firm, operating out of one office in Charlotte, NC, is a unified team of investment professionals possessing extensive industry experience and a proven ability to accelerate growth at our portfolio companies. We are focused on building long-term value and executing on the strategies that have made us successful since 1988.


Doing the Right Thing
Our investment professionals are committed to maintaining the highest ethical standards in everything we do. We believe in communicating with transparency, delivering hard messages openly and quickly, and always having a sense of humility in our dealings with others. We are focused on doing what we say and ensuring that our partners – portfolio managers, industry participants and investors – can trust that we will always do the right thing.




Team
We believe there is no substitute for the experience gained through investing together in hundreds of businesses and across multiple economic cycles.
